{"tid":1679180,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【恥笑，TVB連累廣告商】今日洗版任務 - 鈣思健","createTime":"2019-10-28T05:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T03:39:49.000Z","uid":267969,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"e1c47477391a6abe5086b7e81716bcaf2ed6bc11","tid":1679180,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:01:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>轟炸電郵任務，#2 有詳細點人數</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第3️⃣批電郵：167 --&gt; <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>179人</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第4️⃣批電郵：133 --&gt; <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>147人</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(請補做：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2PkEVlb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PkEVlb&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD5wZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=9e51a142\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2PkEVlb</a>)<br />\n<blockquote>如果email打晒回頭、或者Gmail唔俾send<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. 轉email title<br />\n2. 轉用Yahoo / Hotmail<br />\n3. 電郵title隔空格，請自行創作：強 烈 要 求 不 與 無 綫 電 視 簽 訂 廣 告 合 約<br />\n4. 電郵內容隔空格<br />\nTemplate - <a href=\"https://lih.kg/mJvbgkX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/mJvbgkX</a></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每日洗版行動，真係work ga！<br />\nBless 上星期回應網民洗版</span></strong></span><br />\n喺TVB落廣告就係有咁嘅risk，本來醜聞冇人想知、冇人理、亦冇人爆料，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但公司一落TVB廣告助紂為虐，就會受到注意，醜聞就會被挖出嚟無限廣傳</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/73413228_483660285824159_1781793914622050304_n.png?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_eui2=AeGJ7VD5-avOh6hLsKJSJQ1qgCixpdMjyARA-hTyeIX9Oo1elSDDij6k-CeALV0SFEDoFohVxLwd9roxQPOykFXAB_LyAOCUaQniL-zBN9N28g&amp;_nc_oc=AQlTz-7qgJL1xOT8iEKmRjkT1EtFCsZ_ECRNwwRVpUWFv8yz-abG-eY9i3Y5Z4dw4Vc&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=d4e93f1aeb85245c09a16506ddbd5134&amp;oe=5E2178C5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F73413228_483660285824159_1781793914622050304_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_eui2%3DAeGJ7VD5-avOh6hLsKJSJQ1qgCixpdMjyARA-hTyeIX9Oo1elSDDij6k-CeALV0SFEDoFohVxLwd9roxQPOykFXAB_LyAOCUaQniL-zBN9N28g%26_nc_oc%3DAQlTz-7qgJL1xOT8iEKmRjkT1EtFCsZ_ECRNwwRVpUWFv8yz-abG-eY9i3Y5Z4dw4Vc%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3Dd4e93f1aeb85245c09a16506ddbd5134%26oe%3D5E2178C5&h=a51d253e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n【抵制CCTVB 每日任務】<br />\n1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.<span style=\"color: red;\">推post</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    <br />\n <br />\n是日精選@28 Oct 2019 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>鈣思健</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Calcichew.HK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCalcichew.HK%2F&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD5wZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=11f312b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Calcichew.HK/</a></span></strong><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>※新留言template，全力阻止廣告商簽訂下年合約</strong> <br />\n</span></span>無綫新聞，歪曲事實，出賣港人！本人明白貴公司或已簽訂今年合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故暫時罷用。請貴公司承諾不簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約，不以無綫藝人代言，否則將列入「永久抵制名單」，永不錄用。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/75226517_483623575827830_6187804879935766528_o.png?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_eui2=AeHmdvj5_EKxbgPbGBzRwq0BspugRQY6crPOPmEvtG5mKDOgBm1sqGLjYNZf5dDGxihdqZ-YuZqhv0_emd